title: Storybook for my Daughter; Veganism for Kids, etc.
description: How can you talk about veganism with young children?  This video answers a question from a viewer on this issue, and, also, reads out the script for my children's book on the topic (a picture book that is not yet illustrated, as of Oct. 2016).
